      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to my doctor eventually but they are so hard to get an appointment with and i hate having to go in all the time just for a quick check. since i've been eating way more greens and staying consistent with everything, i just feel like my blood is already 'thin' enough. wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg be a safe way to just maintain where i am without all the extra medicine? it seems like a logical step if my lifestyle is better now",
